========================
DroidSync
========================

A script to sync a playlist from iTunes with a folder (on your Android phone)

To get started, grab sync.py using either git or wget:

# With git:
git clone git://github.com/almonteb/DroidSync.git

# With wget:
wget -O sync.py http://github.com/almonteb/DroidSync/raw/master/sync.py

Then, pick a playlist and sync it:

python sync.py Droid /Volumes/Droid/Music

And pick a stack there!

